## Menus Admin

Dashboard, Véhicules, Marques, Hero, Rendez-vous, Devis, Messages, Avis, Services SAV, Configuration

## Conventions

- Backend: ES Modules, async/await
- Frontend: TypeScript, "use client", Tailwind CSS
- Images: backend/uploads/ avec CORS
- Ports: Backend 5001, Frontend 3000
